body_text: With this new entry in package.json, you can require the font-awesome library easily in bundlers tools like webpack because it resolves directly to the correct file ( like normalize.css do )
Had some trouble finding the ban icon for the first time. I believe these filters could be useful.

This PR changes the print layout, showing three icons per row instead of
one. In this way we can solve an issue with the Bootstrap grid, which
for some reason limits the output to three pages when printing the
cheatsheet.
Fix: #10395
Before: Font Awesome Cheatsheet.pdf
After: Font Awesome Cheatsheet (2).pdf
Would be nice to find the fa-fort-awesome icon by searching for a castle....

This is a very minor change.
I just updated some links using http that go to websites that autoredirect to an https version.
Now they just use https directly so users don't get redirected. ^ _ ^
consolidate Viacoin formatting to be in line with formatting of Bitcoin and other currencies
